/*
=============================================================
Create Database and Schemas
=============================================================

EN:
This script initializes the DataWarehouse environment in SQL Server.
It checks whether the 'DataWarehouse' database already exists. If it does,
the database will be dropped and recreated. After that, the script creates
three schemas used in the Medallion Architecture: 'bronze', 'silver', and 'gold'.

ID:
Script ini digunakan untuk menyiapkan environment DataWarehouse di SQL Server.
Script akan memeriksa apakah database 'DataWarehouse' sudah ada. Jika sudah ada,
database tersebut akan dihapus dan dibuat ulang. Setelah itu, script akan membuat
tiga schema yang digunakan dalam Arsitektur Medallion, yaitu 'bronze', 'silver', dan 'gold'.

-------------------------------------------------------------
WARNING | PERINGATAN
-------------------------------------------------------------

EN:
Running this script will permanently delete the entire 'DataWarehouse' database
if it already exists. All stored data will be lost. Make sure you have a proper
backup before executing this script.

ID:
Menjalankan script ini akan menghapus seluruh database 'DataWarehouse' secara permanen
jika database tersebut sudah ada. Semua data yang tersimpan akan hilang. Pastikan
Anda sudah memiliki backup yang sesuai sebelum menjalankan script ini.
*/

USE master;
GO

-- Drop and recreate the 'DataWarehouse' database
IF EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM sys.databases WHERE name = 'DataWarehouse')
BEGIN
    ALTER DATABASE DataWarehouse SET SINGLE_USER WITH ROLLBACK IMMEDIATE;
    DROP DATABASE DataWarehouse;
END;
GO

-- Create the 'DataWarehouse' database
CREATE DATABASE DataWarehouse;
GO

USE DataWarehouse;
GO

-- Create Schemas
CREATE SCHEMA bronze;
GO

CREATE SCHEMA silver;
GO

CREATE SCHEMA gold;
GO
